  "text": "Our attempt to obtain support for the [CITATION_1] hypothesis by creating, in TVMV, the DAS CP and CSC HC motifs that are present in the aphid-transmissible PSbMV proved unsuccessful. It should be noted that the context in which this motif lies in the TVMV mutant differs from that in PSbMV ; thus the inability of the CSC motif to function in transmission of TVMV might also reflect a requirement of an appropriate context.",
